melbourne dagbok.description: My travel blog from my exchange semester in Ausralia, Melbourne. During my travels I uploaded posts and pictures of my life down under. This website uses sanity and tailwindCSS in React.

memories.description: Website for uploading my pictures that I am proud of via sanity. This website is built in React and tailwindCSS.

echo webkom.description: Webkom is a sub-group of our student association under the Department of Informatics at University in Bergen. Webkom runs the student association's websites.
